name: It's Safe Up Here
description:
While it is safe in the skies, you can only stay up there for so long.

Scavenge, save, and survive in this short and sweet endurance roguelite. Can you make it to the city center?

Jam Disclaimer: This game was made for the Cowboy $100 Game Jam in under one week by myself. Theme is "End of the World".

Due to time constraints, the game does not feature any sound.
